ygData.subject: Re: Gull Skytalon
ygData.msgSnippet: The birds con low green to me (starlings/turacos/tanagers) with the occasional blue quetzel.  I only get XP for about 1 in 40 birds I kill, I am 30th level.
ygData.messageBody:
The birds con low green to me (starlings/turacos/tanagers) with the
occasional blue quetzel. I only get XP for about 1 in 40 birds I kill, I am
30th level. I'm guessing Gull is a rare spawn because a friend and I killed
every d#$% bird on the island and Gull did not show up.

Oh well, I'll try just killing the roamers and leave the birds in the
towers, camps, and diving boards alone. I've been having to destroy copper
and silver to keep from getting encumbered, what a pain.
